				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Pain and Suffering - check this out</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=113892"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">Uniin</a> | 
		                        4/18/2000 10:57:14 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Ok, in the Paineel newbie area there is a ledge on the far side that no one can get up onto. I tried standing on the tree next to the ledge and shadowstepping onto the ledge(i was sick of collecting bone chips). After about 6 tries i finally made it and on top of the ledge there is an invis &quot;thing&quot; there called Pain and Suffering. When i got onto the ledge i had Deadeye on so i don't know of it is possible to see without some kind of see invis on. Even with Deadeye all i saw was the name. It conned indiff to me(erudite necro) but i couldn't con it by right clicking, i had to click on it and push c.  It was red to me at lvl 18, go figure. If anyone knows what this is for plz post it because i am really curious. Thanks.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
