				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Pain and suffering has been in the game since release if you bled to death pain and suffering would try to strike you and you died.<BR>
<BR>
Now as for the !pain and suffering npcs I have seen npcs like that before and been told it just means the NPC is turned off to be worked on or something like that.<BR>
<BR>
The zoning you try to strike a mob message I have also seen. The explanation I was given was if you zone into a zone at the exact same time as a mob dies you get that message.<BR>
